        <item>
            <title>任天堂博物館 10 月京都開幕　可親手製花牌 + 試玩巨型遊戲機</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/20/nintendo-museum-open-in-october/hottopic/walk/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nintendo-museum-open-in-october</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/20/nintendo-museum-open-in-october/hottopic/walk/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 11:00:05 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩樂好去處]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Nintendo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[任天堂]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1257325</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>任天堂位於京都宇治市的博物館將於 2024 年 10 月 2 日正式開幕，成為遊戲迷和歷史愛好者的理想去處。這座博物館將展出任天堂自創立以來的各種硬件和遊戲產品，並設有互動體驗區域，讓參觀者通過遊戲和手作活動深入瞭解這傢俱有悠久歷史的企業。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257344" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/uji_image-694x379.png" alt="" width="694" height="379" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/uji_image-694x379.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/uji_image.png 860w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲任天堂宇治工廠，圖片來源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257336" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image01-580x580.png" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image01-580x580.png 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image01.png 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image01-144x144.png 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p>博物館的展覽將涵蓋任天堂的早期作品如花牌，以及從 NES 到 Wii 等經典遊戲機的發展歷程。參觀者更可以自費親手製作花牌，體驗傳統遊戲的魅力。除此之外，博物館還設置了巨型的遊戲控制器，讓參觀者以別樣的方式重温經典遊戲。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257338" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image03-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image03-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image03.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image03-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲參觀者可親手製作傳統花牌，圖片來源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257337" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image02-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image02-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image02.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image02-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲博物館內設有互動區域，圖片來源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257346" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image06-694x407.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="407" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image06-694x407.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image06.jpg 1160w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲設有特大遊戲機讓參觀者體驗經典遊戲，圖片來源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257347" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image08-694x407.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="407" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image08-694x407.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image08.jpg 1160w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲巨型的遊戲控制器，圖片來源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p>博物館內還有咖啡店，供應特製甜點和自選食材搭配的漢堡，並設有紀念品商店，提供限量版商品。值得一提的是，入館證將採用參觀者的 Mii 角色作為入場識別，並能保留在館內的互動體驗記錄，讓整個參觀過程更加個性化。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257340" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide01-694x453.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="453" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide01-694x453.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide01.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲博物館內的咖啡店，圖片來源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257339" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide02-694x453.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="453" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide02-694x453.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide02.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257341" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide011-694x453.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="453" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide011-694x453.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/image_slide011.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p>門票採用抽選制度，參觀者需要提前通過任天堂博物館的官方網站進行抽選，選中後繳納門票費用即可獲得參觀資格。票價方面，成人票價為 3,300 日圓（約港幣 175 元）、中學生和高中生為 2,200 日圓（約港幣 116）元，小學生票價為 1,100 日圓（約港幣 58 元），未滿學齡的幼童可免費入場。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257343" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820153157-694x295.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="295" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820153157-694x295.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820153157.jpg 1012w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲門票售價，圖片來源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p>任天堂官方博物館網站：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257335" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820152649-694x517.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="517" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820152649-694x517.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820152649.jpg 1209w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257345" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820153507-694x578.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="578" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820153507-694x578.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240820153507.jpg 1081w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲博物館位置，圖片來源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://museum.nintendo.com/en/index.html">Nintendo Museum</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/24/nonofficial-nintendo-kawaii/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">非官方「Nintendo Kawaii」面世　Wii 主機迷你化變鎖匙扣大小</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/20/nintendo-museum-open-in-october/hottopic/walk/">任天堂博物館 10 月京都開幕　可親手製花牌 + 試玩巨型遊戲機</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
